description: I have 7 years’ experience forward deployed supporting USCENTCOM / USSOCOM operations as a linguist/analyst with joint special operations forces and inter-agency partners. I am fluent in Urdu, Dari, Pashto, Farsi languages and have demonstrated a strong proficiency in Punjabi. I have participated in tactical interrogations, conducted polygraph sessions and provided assistance with foreign new hire development activities. I have encountered and adapted difficult tribal dialects of Pashto such as Waziri/khosti and has provided excellent language support for specific Intel groups. I have also provided expert analytical linguistic skills by assisting in SIGINT operations and the production of over 2000 time and sensitive technical reports.
